Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.34,0:02:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,墓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.60,0:02:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这么多的朋友和伙伴都…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.73,0:02:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这些…是你一个人埋葬的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么漠然地一个人埋的么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.22,0:02:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你是魔女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.37,0:02:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么…这么多人都不得不葬身此地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,为素昧平生的你们祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.82,0:03:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 这是要去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.95,0:03:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.58,0:03:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.77,0:03:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.26,0:03:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,黎可斯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.13,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(786,995)}λύκος
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,「黎可斯」不是我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.59,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(932,995)}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,是这个叫做「魂形」的生物的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,生物？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:58.13,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(778,995)}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,魂形… 灵魂的形状
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.90,0:04:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,是以人的「感情」为食的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.82,0:04:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们把自己的感情
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:07.78,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(900,995)}λύκος
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.36,0:04:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,交给这个「黎可斯」作为它的养分
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.49,0:04:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们的心灵平淡如水
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:17.08,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(602,995)}νοῦς
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.16,0:04:17.08,Default,,0,0,0,,发现魂形的人类 把自己的感情交给了它们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.13,0:04:20.01,Default,,0,0,0,,因为感情会让世界毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是不需要的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.72,0:04:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,在你们所渴望了解的外面的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:30.60,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1398,995)}απάθεια
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,没有感情的人们操纵着没有心灵的傀儡士兵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.99,0:04:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,进行着无尽的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.25,0:04:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你们所希冀的东西 难道会在我们的世界里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.32,0:04:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,留下我回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.57,0:04:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我要只身一人 死在这座船上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.23,0:04:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,黎可斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.65,0:04:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我倒是无所谓
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.77,0:04:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,管他战争什么的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.91,0:04:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不想一辈子被关在泥鲸上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.54,0:04:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,要是能从那里解脱…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.46,0:05:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我的感情什么的要多少给多少
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.17,0:05:03.78,Default,,0,0,0,,欧尼！ 不行 危险…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.87,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.95,0:05:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.02,0:05:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有成百… 上千的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.54,0:05:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不计其数的人的「心灵」从我脑海里穿流而过 随之消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.41,0:05:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对了 这是… 这个混沌是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.78,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\pos(930,995)}hypergraphia
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.66,0:05:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}当我无法停止书写时
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.21,0:05:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}脑海中浮现的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.40,0:05:41.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}贝妮希…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.92,0:05:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不行 这是我的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.65,0:05:50.03,Default,,0,0,0,,就算是悲伤的感情 我也不想忘却
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.67,0:05:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,黎可斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你们知道自己做了些什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.03,0:06:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,查克罗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.28,0:06:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.64,0:06:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,查克罗？ 查克罗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.50,0:06:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,啊… 莎米？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.48,0:06:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,你们看到了许许多多的墓碑…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.25,0:06:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,真的仅此而已吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.56,0:06:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.43,0:06:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,查克罗呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.60,0:06:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,是的 别的什么都没…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了 就相信你们说的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.19,0:06:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,台霞 告诉大家
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.38,0:06:47.68,Default,,0,0,0,,今后一律禁止前往那座岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.74,0:06:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 物资的搜集就…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.66,0:06:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一针一线都不许拿
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:56.60,Default,,0,0,0,,待这冷静冷静
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.32,0:07:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,欧尼你没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那时候 没有被吸走心灵吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.48,0:07:29.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊 那时候看到了奇怪的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.32,0:07:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…真的是会夺取心灵的生物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.56,0:07:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.70,0:07:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,只看到了一刹那
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,外面的世界的战争
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.44,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(872,995)}thymia
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.73,0:07:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,是情念力的战争吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.42,0:07:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那个女的也会用的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,欧尼 不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你也见到了那些坟墓吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.92,0:07:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我啊 开始觉得外面的世界有点可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.35,0:07:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,说回来 你那时候怎么不拉我一把
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.02,0:08:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,要不是黎可斯救了我…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.24,0:08:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以我们的心灵平淡如水
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.46,0:08:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,可是这样的话 为什么要救我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.19,0:08:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,查克罗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.07,0:08:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,玛索
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.33,0:08:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我这就吃…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.91,0:08:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不是 是释放
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.66,0:08:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只有你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.75,0:08:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,有人看到了你是被欧尼强行拖过去的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然并不完全是被强迫的…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你运气不错啊 赶在这个节骨眼上被放出来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.38,0:08:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.76,0:08:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,查克罗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有一种被称为「星蝗」的大型蝗虫栖息在泥鲸周围
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.98,0:08:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}他们以泥鲸的废弃物为食谋生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.95,0:08:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}当它们的种群密度升高后 就会变成适合长期移动的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在深夜发出光亮 开始大迁徙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.37,0:09:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我们将之称为「飞蝗现象」
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:07.31,Default,,0,0,0,,抓紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.97,0:09:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,天黑之前得抢到好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.21,0:09:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,莎米 涅兹 洛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.68,0:09:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思 请稍微等我一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.88,0:09:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,喂 查克罗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.75,0:09:22.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你去哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.79,0:09:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,请问您怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,您的伤口还痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.82,0:09:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我是这座塔上负责照顾长老们生活的奈莉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.30,0:09:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然我只是「无印」 但如果有什么要求请不要客气
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,请告诉长老们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.58,0:09:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我离不开那座船
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.48,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1016,995)}λύκος
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.34,0:09:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,让我回到「黎可斯」身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能离开它
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,当我有了感情…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,会让我不胜其苦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.02,0:10:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,不把心灵抹杀掉的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.31,0:10:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,人有心灵才是普通的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.92,0:10:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,你很快就会适应的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.78,0:10:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,查克罗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.87,0:10:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,奈莉 拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,能让我把黎可斯带出去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,带出去…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.98,0:10:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你还想被关到体内去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.46,0:10:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我想跟她一起看飞蝗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.46,0:10:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,想让黎可斯… 和我的朋友一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.55,0:10:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,奈莉也早点去找个好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.15,0:10:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.98,0:10:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.10,0:10:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,哪怕你没有心灵 我也放不下你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.75,0:10:53.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你孤身一人 为那么多的伙伴修了坟墓
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.53,0:10:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的女孩子 我怎么能置之不理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,咦 让黎可斯也来？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.84,0:11:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那个岛上的姑娘？ 不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你好 我叫涅兹
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.71,0:11:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,然后 你打算怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.68,0:11:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要是被谁发现了 就不止是看不了飞蝗这么简单了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.31,0:11:22.13,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.76,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,把我的防沙斗篷给她套上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,就认不出是谁了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我说你啊 洗都不洗的斗篷就这么给女孩子穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 还是还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.70,0:11:37.79,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 可是这样就露馅了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.03,0:11:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,第4塔的顶上还空着
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,咱们去那吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.54,0:11:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 我不行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.63,0:11:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,累了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.92,0:11:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就到顶上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.55,0:11:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.39,0:12:00.13,Default,,0,0,0,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.26,0:12:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,查克罗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.26,0:12:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,抱我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.07,0:12:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你…你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,上次不就抱我上去了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.06,0:12:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs57}上次…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.17,0:12:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,上次飞蝗是三年前的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs57}抱我 走不动了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.23,0:12:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,抱不动了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.71,0:12:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,莎米都这么重了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.48,0:12:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,莎米才不重呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.53,0:12:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,查克罗就知道欺负人！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,白痴！ 小气鬼！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.70,0:12:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,瞧 这不是还走得动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.30,0:12:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,莎米 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.71,0:12:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,要我背你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不用
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.54,0:12:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,小虫虫 还没到吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.79,0:12:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,再加加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.49,0:12:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,这样就快了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.40,0:13:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,玛索 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.75,0:13:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.37,0:13:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,自从我家小子在沙海事故里走了以后
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.46,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,我就一直放不下小孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.25,0:13:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,那个 库奇巴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,好痛的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.13,0:13:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,手 捏得太紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,啊 不…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.04,0:13:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,还没来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.07,0:13:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.44,0:13:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,…你看到了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.44,0:13:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,蝗虫？ 在哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.30,0:13:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我七岁的时候被送去军队的培训学校
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.31,0:13:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我和家人一起去的学校宿舍
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那天我就和他们永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.45,0:13:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但对于没有感情的我们来说 并没有留下什么感慨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,通往宿舍的道路又长又陡 行李还很重
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:13:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.42,0:14:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样怎么当个优秀的军人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.96,0:14:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,看到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.38,0:14:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.73,0:14:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,在那个生物里 看到了那个时候的你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.33,0:14:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我一直… 觉得那是无所谓的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.25,0:14:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 如今会如此伤感…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:14:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,黎可斯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你 确实有着心灵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.57,0:15:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你和我们是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.47,0:15:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 说不定有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.87,0:15:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,泥鲸会漂游到你家人附近
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.73,0:15:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,而且在泥鲸这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,征召入伍 战死沙场这种事情是不会发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.28,0:15:25.53,Default,,0,0,0,,黎可斯 在这里生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.17,0:15:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,查克罗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.23,0:15:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.89,0:15:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我…有件事情必须要告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.85,0:15:39.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这座船…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.94,0:15:40.55,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:46.72,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(932,995)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.98,0:15:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,「法莱那」…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,这些虫子…是要去哪里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也好想去个遥远的世界啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.13,0:16:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}砂刑历93年7月8日
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.18,0:16:20.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}确认飞蝗现象
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.53,0:16:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虫群在泥鲸上空不断飞舞发光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.45,0:16:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而到黎明时分则启程向着沙海远方飞去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.32,0:16:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,查克罗！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.42,0:16:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,快给我起来 吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.33,0:16:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,啊够了 你这家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.87,0:16:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,给我像话点！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我早就受够跟你一班了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:54.32,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1230,995)}destroyer
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.54,0:16:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,尽给人家添麻烦 你这毁灭者
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.76,0:16:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我说啊 托比
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.19,0:17:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,自从我们父母去世
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们开始共同生活以后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.31,0:17:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我可没少帮你照看弟弟妹妹哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.52,0:17:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是彼此彼此么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.36,0:17:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,查克罗 漏嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,这是谁照看谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.70,0:17:18.95,Default,,0,0,0,,还有脸说彼此彼此！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.95,0:17:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我今天要去种田
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.25,0:17:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,苏澳
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.89,0:17:29.02,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.39,0:17:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哇 哥哥一身泥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.97,0:17:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我比大家干活慢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.47,0:17:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,所以先来干活了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.35,0:17:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,哥哥什么都好 就是运动神经不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去播种吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天的飞蝗 好漂亮呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.24,0:17:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.57,0:17:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那之后 黎可斯怎么样了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.11,0:17:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,送她回中央塔了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.66,0:18:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟是悄悄带出来的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,莎米 查克罗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.65,0:18:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.58,0:18:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我要去帮长老会做事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.36,0:18:14.17,Default,,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.71,0:18:18.83,Default,,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.56,0:18:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,奈莉？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.27,0:18:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,苏澳
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.23,0:18:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.82,0:18:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,黎可斯说有话要传达给各位长老
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.32,0:18:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,看起来很是焦虑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.82,0:18:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,可是 长老会却拒绝跟她见面…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.10,0:18:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,据说…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.37,0:18:50.72,Default,,0,0,0,,长老会瞒着台霞阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.87,0:18:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,派警备团出海加强了周边的警备
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.55,0:18:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我去见她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.14,0:19:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,有人把门 说是谁都不让见她的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.60,0:19:08.05,Default,,0,0,0,,请问有何贵干？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,不能进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我得到了许可
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.90,0:19:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我 我怎么不知…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.43,0:19:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你现在知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.28,0:19:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.70,0:19:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰了 我是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.43,0:19:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你 带我去见这座岛的代表
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.79,0:19:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我有很重要的…必须要告诉你们的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.15,0:19:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,那告诉我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,台霞姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,查克罗的记录飞跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.76,0:19:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,得去捡回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我派人去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.60,0:19:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子说想了解世界
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,所以要留下记录
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.85,0:19:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,如今 我也怀着同样的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:19:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:20:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,长老会把漂流岛上的少女藏起来不让我们相见
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.04,0:20:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,没有办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,泥鲸的领导权 依惯例是掌握在长老会手中的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.29,0:20:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,年满61岁的全体无印 都会成为长老会的成员
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.01,0:20:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,并能得知泥鲸的历史以及它与世界的关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.14,0:20:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,首长并没有政治实权
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.51,0:20:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,只是为了塑造一个受民众爱戴的对象
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.21,0:20:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我还有19年才能进入长老会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.06,0:20:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,在那之前 我都像木偶一般
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.39,0:20:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,不得不饰演受人崇拜的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.75,0:20:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有…有什么不好的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.46,0:20:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不管台霞姐姐是木偶还是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.08,0:20:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我都永远支持你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.73,0:20:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,只要是为了泥鲸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,让我成为一个好的木偶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.98,0:21:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:17.02,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(776,995)}σκύλος
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.39,0:21:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,斯奇洛斯 展开作战行动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.11,0:21:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,快从这里逃走 越快越好！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.73,0:21:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这座岛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:22.93,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(932,995)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.18,0:21:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,「法莱那」…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.65,0:21:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,查克罗 那是沙海豚么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.88,0:21:32.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:39.44,GREEK11,,0,0,0,,{\pos(717,995)}φάλαινα
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.14,0:21:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,「鲸的罪人」 将会被攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.58,0:21:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,罪人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.90,0:21:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是罪人？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.27,0:21:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我作为工作留下的正式记录
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.68,0:22:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}到今天为止了
